title: NFL Around the League: July 31, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: July 31, 2013
description:
On a busy day inside the NFL media newsroom, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling sit down in NFL.com's Studio 66 to discuss the biggest news from coast to coast. Topics include Percy Harvin's injury, Riley Cooper's racially insensitive remark and more.
